* [[Tar-Aldarion|Aldarion]] returns from a fourteen year long voyage from [[Middle-earth]] with ships that were battered and broken by the seas. He had first sailed to the haven of [[Vinyalondë]] and then sailed along the coasts southwards, far beyond any place that had been reached by the ships of the [[Númenóreans]] before. On his return northwards, he had encountered great storms, scarcely escaped shipwreck in the [[Harad]] and found Vinyalondë overthrown by great seas and plundered by hostile men.<ref>{{UT|Wife}}, first pages and NOTES, ''Chronology''</ref>

